skins.shipDescription: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40 Unlock build after receiving
skins.selfIntroduction: The offshoot of the County-class, the Norfolk-class, includes me and my sisters. My proudest achievement was giving chase to Bismarck and not letting my sister's intel go to waste. I am still far from matching her, so I must become a sister she can be proud of!
skins.acquisition: Hello, I'm Norfolk's little sister, Dorsetshire~! I look more mature than my sister? Surely you jest! She's my role model!
skins.login: Welcome back~ What are we going to do today?
skins.details: My big sister is definitely cuter, at least compared to me.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Is it not common knowledge that my big sister is the cutest in the world?
skins.secretaryIdle2: For allowing me to use the intel my sister gave me, Bismarck is such a generous person.
skins.secretaryIdle3: If it's about my sister, I could speak for three days and three nights and still not be done.
skins.secretaryTouch: So, Commander, you think I'm actually a bit too big?
